message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Code · Cyberpunk Store</title>
    <!-- Font futuristico -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:opsz@14..32&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #0a0f1e, #03050a);
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            color: #e0f0ff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        /* main wrapper – vetro cyberpunk */
        .cyber-card {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(12, 20, 35, 0.55);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px) saturate(180%);
            border: 1px solid #33f0ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba#33f0ff, 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.3);
            border-radius: 2rem 0.5rem 2rem 0.5rem;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cyber-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 60px #33f0ff, 0 0 30px #00ffcc;
        }

        /* griglia layout */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem 1.5rem;
            align-items: start;
        }

        /* hero */
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b3f0ff, #33f0ff, #a66eff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .hero .sub {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #b0d9ff;
            border-left: 3px solid #33f0ff;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #c0d0f0;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        .feature-list {
            margin-top: 1.8rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            padding: 0.4rem 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #2a4a6a;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: "▸";
            color: #33f0ff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        /* pulsanti / cta */
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #33f0ff;
            color: #33f0ff;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
            margin-top: 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 0 1.2rem 0 1.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #33f0ff;
            color: #0a0f1e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #33f0ff;
            border-color: #b3f0ff;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* modulo contatti */
        .contact-module {
            background: rgba(0, 10, 30, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid #33f0ff;
            border-radius: 1.5rem 0.2rem 1.5rem 0.2rem;
            padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.05);
        }

        .contact-module h3 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #b3f0ff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px #33f0ff;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: #99ccff;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            background: #0e1a2b;
            border: 1px solid #2a5a7a;
            border-radius: 0.4rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 0.9rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #e0f0ff;
            outline: none;
            transition: border 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            border-color: #33f0ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(51, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }

